ast.name: Word Mage
ast.comment:
Word Mage is an educational game with fruit ninja style gameplay that tests students knowledge of nouns, verbs, adjectives and adverbs.

#StoneHack2013

body.text: The board is a 2D canvas with a physics engine. Gravity makes sprites fall and boundary makes them bounce.
Display the board. The game loop will start after leaving main.
Check if the game should end
